name: DariaSidorko/FinstagramApp
description: This is a MERN stack social network application that features most popular Instagram functions such as registering, creating profile, post images, like images, leave comments, bookmark posts, update profile, track new likes and follow other profiles. Node JS, React, Express and Mongo DB were used to build it that was integrated with React Router and Redux. Postman was used for testing application API’s. The application was deployed using Heroku CLI. Other technologies and libraries used: npm development tool, passport js, Mongoose MongoDB, JSON Web Token, gravatar api, axios, bcrypt.js.
